I mean, like...

1252
01:17:15,068 --> 01:17:20,568
What kind of person
was he before he got married?

1253
01:17:20,578 --> 01:17:27,809
Like, back in high school
when you knew him,

1254
01:17:27,819 --> 01:17:31,046
'cause, um...

1255
01:17:31,056 --> 01:17:33,051
Uh...

1256
01:17:37,023 --> 01:17:43,558
I can't imagine him,

1257
01:17:43,568 --> 01:17:49,668
you know, like,
without my mom.

1258
01:17:55,175 --> 01:17:58,873
He didn't judge people.

1259
01:17:58,883 --> 01:18:02,377
And he was, um--

1260
01:18:02,387 --> 01:18:05,980
he was--he was smart.

1261
01:18:05,990 --> 01:18:09,117
Smart, real smart,

1262
01:18:09,127 --> 01:18:15,223
but he didn't, you know,
show off about it.

1263
01:18:15,233 --> 01:18:17,487
<i>He was just</i>
<i>a really pleasant person</i>

1264
01:18:17,497 --> 01:18:19,765
