and whatnot and I'm thinking,

1277
01:18:50,897 --> 01:18:53,556
"you know, you're just
encouraging them to drive fast."

1278
01:18:53,566 --> 01:18:56,326
But you, you got yourself
a great car here.

1279
01:18:56,336 --> 01:18:57,727
If I bought one
for my own daughter,

1280
01:18:57,737 --> 01:19:00,335
you know it's reliable.

1281
01:19:00,345 --> 01:19:02,632
Thank you
for putting it all together.

1282
01:19:02,642 --> 01:19:05,468
Any problems, any concerns,
you just give me a call.

1283
01:19:05,478 --> 01:19:07,478
